imdb.plot outline: He's a stand-up comedian, an internet sensation and a self-proclaimed 'city slicker'. So, Neel Kolhatkar is heading to the bush to meet the locals and put his nose to the grindstone. Can he hack it though? Sheep shearing, pigeon racing, bow hunting, rally driving and bull riding aren't exactly for the faint hearted. Well, maybe pigeon racing - But Neel gets to experience an Australia that most Aussies never see and at the same time, he's feeding his stand-up schtick too. Saddle up for Virgin Bush.
